WorldStage Newsonline– Neimeth International Pharmaceuticals Plc, a manufacturer of and marketer of pharmaceuticals and animal health products has  announced plans to raise additional equity to the tune of N5 billion. In a notification at the Nigerian Stock Exchange (NSE) for the investing public signed by Florence Onyenekwe Mrs, Company Secretary on Monday, the company said that the board took the decision at its meeting of 15th January 2021. The notice said the  resolution will be presented at Annual General Meeting on 9th March 2021.